'''Lumguzzling''' was a type of drinking competition that made use of the drink [[Lum/Legends|lum]], which, while [[Alcohol/Legends|alcoholic]], was impossible to overdose on. It was an activity popular in the [[Corellian sector/Legends|Corellian sector]], but was known throughout [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]].

Participants would take turns drinking entire pitchers of lum, which cost approximately 6 to 10 [[Galactic Credit Standard/Legends|credits]] apiece during the time of the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. The last person remaining conscious would be deemed the winner.

During the early [[Standard year/Legends|years]] of the [[Imperial Era/Legends|Imperial Era]], at a launch party to commemorate the launch of [[Hovertrain/Legends|hover train]] ''[[Gem of Alderaan]]'' on the [[Planet/Legends|world]] of [[Alderaan/Legends|Alderaan]], several attendees including the [[Twi'lek/Legends|Twi'lek]] fashion designer [[Lynaa]] held a lumguzzling contest within the train's [[Nightclub/Legends|nightclub]] [[Decadence nightclub|Decadence]].<ref name="The Gem of Alderaan">{{DoD|The Gem of Alderaan}}</ref>

